WEBVTT

00:00:28.403 --> 00:00:30.386
Bili smo gladni.

00:00:31.586 --> 00:00:35.077
Tada je djevojka u plavoj uniformi

00:00:35.101 --> 00:00:38.657
došla u moje selo s Ujedinjenim nacijama

00:00:38.681 --> 00:00:40.459
kako bi nahranili djecu.

00:00:41.784 --> 00:00:44.363
Dok mi je dodavala kašu,

00:00:44.387 --> 00:00:47.648
pitala sam zašto je ovdje

00:00:47.672 --> 00:00:51.362
i bez oklijevanja je rekla:

00:00:51.386 --> 00:00:58.044
"Kao Afrikanke, 
moramo uzdići sve ljude u Africi."

00:00:59.705 --> 00:01:02.737
Nisam imala pojma šta je željela reći.